     <p>主持人</p> 
     <div class="story_djs_items"> 
      <a target="_blank" href="http://www.g-cores.com/users/38146"> <img class="img-circle" src="http://alioss.g-cores.com/uploads/user/f9e1007b-bae5-4ab4-8f3d-64a415225f8a_normal.jpg" alt="F9e1007b bae5 4ab4 8f3d 64a415225f8a normal" /> <br /> 兔子瞧 </a> 
      <a target="_blank" href="http://www.g-cores.com/users/20803"> <img class="img-circle" src="http://alioss.g-cores.com/uploads/user/30736af9-9596-46e4-b83f-72ad89d648e4_normal.jpg" alt="30736af9 9596 46e4 b83f 72ad89d648e4 normal" /> <br /> 四十二 </a> 
      <a target="_blank" href="http://www.g-cores.com/users/3"> <img class="img-circle" src="http://alioss.g-cores.com/uploads/user/d95bb3d6-38e4-4f24-9100-9b05f6a74c89_normal.jpg" alt="D95bb3d6 38e4 4f24 9100 9b05f6a74c89 normal" /> <br /> 西蒙 </a> 
